@node FAQ "What, How, When...?"

Q: Descent exits with "Not enough strings in text file" or something like that!
A: You're using pre-V1.4 .pig/.hog-files or the shareware-files which currently don't work with Descent.

Q: Why do the walls look so curious when I fly near them? Am I stoned?
A: This one is fixed with r0.50!

Q: The screenmode requesters don't show up, what's wrong?
A: No problem anymore with r0.62!

Q: When will there be a PPC-version?
A: As soon as I have enough money to buy a PowerUP board.
   But I'll release my sources with r1.00, so there may be other people who want to do this.

Q: Why is the sound that low?
A: With r0.62, the sound is boosted to maximum without distortion...

Q: Descent crashes on my Apollo '060 accelerator!
A: The 68060.library that comes with Apollo boards seems to have some serious bugs, please use the Phase5 ones instead.

@endnode

